{"tid":1508512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街藍絲抹黑在加拿大港人因撐反送中被歧視","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:49:08.000Z","uid":142794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59344f1090ca1eb470dd58a0ac180f2ac65baab2","tid":1508512,"uid":142794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"藍絲老母send咗條錄音去屋企個group<br />\n平時食飯都費時嘈 今舖佢仲大大聲播出嚟<br />\n唔擺上嚟會激鬼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大致係講有個黃到仆街嘅17歲仔啱啱去完加拿大一個月study tour 話個邊啲鬼佬笑啲香港人示威 話班後生低質又暴力 係個邊因爲係香港人所以成日比鬼仔蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到唔敢認做香港人 要扮台灣人喎 翻到香港變藍絲鬧學生鬧老師鬧埋蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後個360度大轉變笑撚死 係咪即係無變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推到個17歲有為少年出嚟講下個經歷 睇下外國有幾睇香港唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋喺愛国藍絲口中聽到「封閉」兩個字都幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fabbe4dad97c699f344c762400391c16d3a194","tid":1508512,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁多呢d無聊人，贏左先再清算啦<br />\n我地而家明星都唔得閒批鬥啦<br />\n推d有用 post好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8940b4530d3e176a373b4a6f95ae80dc947eaf5","tid":1508512,"uid":142794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9fabbe4dad97c699f344c762400391c16d3a194","tid":1508512,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁多呢d無聊人，贏左先再清算啦<br />\n我地而家明星都唔得閒批鬥啦<br />\n推d有用 post好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱聽到太撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid